src:
Foto: Dubay shahzodasi bir oy ichida ikkinchi marta O‘zbekistonga keldi

01 Nov 2019, 22:12

Dubay amirligining valiahdi Shayx Hamdan bin Muhammad Ol Maktum oktabr oyida ikkinchi marta O‘zbekistonga keldi.


Foto: Telegram/Zed News

Telegram’dagi AviaSpotter kanalining ma’lum qilishicha, Dubay hukumatiga xizmat ko‘rsatuvchi Dubai Royal Air Wing samolyoti 31-oktabr, payshanba kuni Toshkentga qo‘ngan.


Foto: Instagram/faz3

Shayx Hamdanning Instagram’ga yuklagan suratlariga ko‘ra, u Tashkent City hududidagi Hilton mehmonxonasiga joylashib, payshanba kuni Toshkent shahar hokimi Jahongir Ortiqxo‘jayev bilan uchrashgan.


Foto: Instagram/faz3

Shahzoda, shuningdek, O‘zbekiston Prezidenti Shavkat Mirziyoyev oilasi vakillarining ham mehmoni bo‘lgan.
Dubay taxti vorisi oktabr oyi o‘rtalarida ham O‘zbekistonda bo‘lib, Navoiy shahridan qariyb 50 kilometr uzoqlikdagi cho‘l hududida lochinlar bilan ov qilgan edi.


Foto: Instagram/faz3

Bu hududda 300 gektar maydonni egallagan “Amirliklarning yo‘rg‘a tuvaloqni asrash markazi” joylashgan.
text:
Photo: Prince of Dubai visits Uzbekistan for the second time in a month

01 Nov 2019, 22:12

Sheikh Hamdan bin Mohammed Al Maktoum, Dubai's Crown Prince arrives in Uzbekistan for the second time in October.


Photo: Telegram / Zed News

AviaSpotter in Telegram reports that Dubai Royal Air Wing, which operates Dubai government, landed in Tashkent on Thursday, October 31.


Photo: Instagram / faz3

According to Sheikh Hamdan's Instagram photos, he was staying at the Hilton Hotel in Tashkent, where he met the mayor of Tashkent Jahongir Ortikhojaev on Thursday.


Photo: Instagram / faz3

The Prince was also a guest of the family of the President of Uzbekistan Shavkat Mirziyoyev.
The heir to the Dubai throne was in Uzbekistan in mid-October, hunting for falcons in the desert about 50 kilometers away from Navoi.


Photo: Instagram / faz3

The UAE is located in the area of 300 hectares.
